1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:43,650
I got it.

4
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,120
I am now using the college's pay phone.

5
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,120
I'm hanging up.

6
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:50,720
[By the way, the girl named Li Qing Tong]

7
00:01:50,810 --> 00:01:52,080
[called me again and asked for you.]

8
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:54,520
[She also left me
the phone number of her dorm.]

9
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,800
[Your father doesn't let me tell you.]

10
00:01:57,289 --> 00:01:58,670
[But I don't think]

11
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,240
[it should be kept from you.]

12
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:01,810
[You've grown up.]

13
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:05,010
[I think I can't ignore your thoughts
like I did before.]

14
00:02:05,330 --> 00:02:07,010
[I'll give you the phone number.]

15
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:08,600
[It's up to you to decide]

16
00:02:09,330 --> 00:02:10,729
[if you want to contact her.]

17
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,410
Hello.

18
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:39,010
Fan Shui Shui.

19
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,040
You haven't contacted me for a long time.

20
00:02:43,170 --> 00:02:43,680
[Episode 18]
[The Return of the Old Days]

21
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,440
How are you doing there?

22
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,640
Do you have a boyfriend?

23
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:56,490
Li Qing Tong.

24
00:02:58,370 --> 00:02:59,960
Would you like to be my girlfriend?

25
00:03:02,010 --> 00:03:02,890
Yes, I'd love to.

26
00:03:24,250 --> 00:03:25,210
Have you thought it through?

27
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,020
Yes.

28
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,000
I choose here.

29
00:03:31,810 --> 00:03:32,730
But there's another problem.

30
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,710
What is the problem?

31
00:03:33,810 --> 00:03:35,840
Are you sure she'll come?

32
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,170
Have you thought it through?

33
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,730
Would I come to you if I haven't?

34
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:46,480
Now that you've thought about it,

35
00:03:46,570 --> 00:03:47,570
try it.

36
00:03:49,010 --> 00:03:50,560
But you have to promise me one thing.

37
00:03:50,890 --> 00:03:51,770
What?

38
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,200
If...

39
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,610
I mean if.

40
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:58,370
If you two get together in the future,

41
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,090
or even get married,

42
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:01,970
you must promise me

43
00:04:02,530 --> 00:04:03,410
not to abandon her.

44
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,680
You can't leave her for any reason.

45
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,610
If you can't do that,

46
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:10,500
I won't agree to you two
being together no matter what.

47
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,480
Li Jin Bu.

48
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,410
I'll only say this to you once.

49
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:20,930
If Li Qing Tong really becomes my wife,

50
00:04:21,690 --> 00:04:23,410
I, Chen Jun He, will only have her

51
00:04:24,010 --> 00:04:25,120
as a wife in this life.

52
00:04:25,850 --> 00:04:26,850
I'll do what I say.

53
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,170
Then you must remember this.

54
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,400
Never forget.

55
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:37,240
Don't you really want to go?

56
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,190
In fact, Chen Jun He is also quite good.

57
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,450
He is not bad.

58
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,960
And

59
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,240
he's much more mature

60
00:04:47,330 --> 00:04:48,720
than he was in high school.

61
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,240
He doesn't give you much trouble
anymore either.

62
00:04:50,610 --> 00:04:52,490
He also gets here for you.

63
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:53,960
He's very sincere.

64
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,760
If you really think you are not suitable,

65
00:04:57,850 --> 00:04:59,090
I will go to reject him.

66
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:00,760
I...

67
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,130
I...

68
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,330
Think about it yourself.

69
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:16,480
It's late.

70
00:06:16,570 --> 00:06:18,610
How come Lao Chen is still not coming?

71
00:07:02,850 --> 00:07:03,730
Sir,

72
00:07:04,010 --> 00:07:05,810
I have a very important thing
to do tonight. Can I...

73
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:07,000
Did I allow you to stand up?

74
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:07,960
Get down.

75
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:27,820
Hello

76
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,280
[Dude, where are you now?]

77
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:30,430
[Help me!]

78
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,430
Xiao Huo.

79
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,400
What's wrong with you?

80
00:07:32,810 --> 00:07:34,400
[Are you Niu Xiao Huo's friend?]

81
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:35,960
Who are you?

82
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,790
[He owes us 30,000 yuan.]

83
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,120
[Do you care or not?]

84
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,370
No... How can he owe you money?

85
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,470
Give him the phone.

86
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,480
[Stop the nonsense.]

87
00:07:43,570 --> 00:07:45,710
[If I don't see the money in half an hour,
I'll cut off one of his hands first.]

88
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,680
Wait.

89
00:07:46,890 --> 00:07:47,770
Where are you?

90
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,120
I'll send the money now.

91
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,960
[Building Materials Market, Qiaonan Road.]

92
00:07:51,409 --> 00:07:52,610
[Call when you arrive.]

93
00:08:04,050 --> 00:08:10,650
[Police Station]

94
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:11,530
Bro.

95
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,650
It's all my fault.

96
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:14,290
Shut up.

97
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,450
Bro, don't be silent.

98
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,560
Niu Xiao Huo.

99
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,810
How old are you?

100
00:08:27,250 --> 00:08:28,930
Can you do something decent in the future?

101
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:31,800
You didn't do well in school, fine.

102
00:08:32,409 --> 00:08:33,650
After graduating, you gamble.

103
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,200
Do you really want to go down like that?

104
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,720
Tonight you just met a few money scammer.

105
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:43,330
If we meet really bad people,
we'll really die, you know?

106
00:08:45,970 --> 00:08:47,520
You just keep falling.

107
00:08:47,610 --> 00:08:48,800
I don't care about you.

108
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,490
Bro, I swear to God.

109
00:08:50,890 --> 00:08:53,210
I, Niu Xiao Huo, will be a good person.

110
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,200
I will work with my uncle
in the renovation team tomorrow.

111
00:08:56,290 --> 00:08:57,650
Please believe me.

112
00:08:58,410 --> 00:08:59,920
It doesn't matter if I believe you or not.

113
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,200
You are not my son.

114
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:03,570
You just need to live up to your parents.

115
00:09:03,770 --> 00:09:04,760
But I have one more thing.

116
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,920
What?

117
00:09:06,530 --> 00:09:09,290
Please don't tell anyone
in the hometown about this.

118
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:13,400
And you know it's very small.

119
00:09:13,490 --> 00:09:15,360
If it spreads

120
00:09:15,450 --> 00:09:17,000
and my mum gets to know about it,

121
00:09:17,090 --> 00:09:18,480
she'll have a heart attack again.

122
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:21,480
I just wanted to get some money
for medical treatment this time.

123
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:22,690
I didn't expect...

124
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:24,810
All right.

125
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:26,090
I got it.

126
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,480
Do you have money?

127
00:09:42,490 --> 00:09:43,410
Take it home quickly.

128
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,880
Work hard with your uncle.

129
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,850
Bro.

130
00:09:53,930 --> 00:09:55,640
I will pay you back the money.

131
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,930
You are a student.

132
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,270
When you encounter this kind of thing,

133
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,470
how can you rush in
and fight with people by yourself?

134
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:38,520
If you have an accident,
what will you do?

135
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:40,850
What will the college tell your family?

136
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,840
I'm sorry.

137
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,480
Go back.

138
00:10:44,890 --> 00:10:45,920
Reflect on it.

139
00:10:58,890 --> 00:11:01,000
Do you know that Li Qing Tong
waited for you the whole night?

140
00:11:03,170 --> 00:11:04,720
Can you be more sincere?

141
00:11:04,810 --> 00:11:05,840
This date

142
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:07,510
was still your initiative.

143
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:10,240
You had to get into a fight at this time?
Can't you settle down a little?

144
00:11:10,330 --> 00:11:13,280
It's not that I had to get into trouble.
It's because of Niu Xiao Huo.

145
00:11:13,370 --> 00:11:14,560
What could I do?

146
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,570
You don't need to explain to me.

147
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,880
I've helped you and Li Qing Tong
many times.

148
00:11:20,970 --> 00:11:23,880
I even put aside my prejudices
and hoped you two would get together.

149
00:11:24,370 --> 00:11:25,250
What's the result?

150
00:11:25,410 --> 00:11:26,400
It's the same every time.

151
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:28,080
You leave her alone.

152
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,040
I can't change fate,

153
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:33,890
and I can't change you.

154
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,410
You need to give yourself an explanation.

155
00:11:36,850 --> 00:11:38,490
How much do you really like Li Qing Tong?

156
00:11:39,810 --> 00:11:41,720
I won't interfere in your affairs
from now on.

157
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,570
What did you do last night?

158
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,570
Li Qing Tong waited for you all night.

159
00:11:59,850 --> 00:12:00,840
What happened to your face?

160
00:12:01,130 --> 00:12:02,370
Who did you fight with?

161
00:12:02,810 --> 00:12:04,720
Shut up and be quiet. Okay?

162
00:12:15,570 --> 00:12:16,450
Li Qing Tong.

163
00:12:24,010 --> 00:12:24,890
Li Qing Tong.

164
00:12:27,130 --> 00:12:28,010
Li Qing Tong.

165
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,850
What happened to your face?

166
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,520
Did you fight again?

167
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,080
No.

168
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:39,080
I was really busy yesterday.

169
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:40,210
It's okay.

170
00:12:41,650 --> 00:12:43,090
I didn't go yesterday anyway.

171
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:45,810
You... You had
more important things to do.

172
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:47,450
We are quite in tune.

173
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:49,720
Yesterday

174
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,160
is behind us.

175
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,350
Wait. Li Qing Tong.

176
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:55,200
You really have to listen
to my explanation this time.

177
00:12:55,290 --> 00:12:56,850
-Yesterday I...
-You don't have to explain this time.

178
00:12:58,130 --> 00:12:59,370
There's no next time anyway.

179
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,400
Hello.

180
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:23,040
[Why do I feel you are in a bad mood
by hearing your voice?]

181
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:27,730
It's a long story.

182
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:30,810
[Don't you and Li Qing Tong
get along quite well?]

183
00:13:31,050 --> 00:13:32,010
[What's wrong with this?]

184
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,480
Let's not talk about it.
Come out for a drink.

185
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:38,000
[I'm just about to say something to you.]

186
00:13:38,650 --> 00:13:40,730
[I'm going elsewhere
for a hands-on activity.]

187
00:13:42,810 --> 00:13:43,810
Go elsewhere?

188
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:45,370
How long will you go for?

189
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,410
[A few weeks.]

190
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:50,850
All right.

191
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,080
Take care of yourself.

192
00:13:52,810 --> 00:13:53,690
I'll wait for you.

193
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,070
[All right.]

194
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,040
[Take care.]

195
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:06,840
Hello.

196
00:14:09,210 --> 00:14:10,590
Li Qing Tong, it's for you.

197
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:12,410
-I'm coming.
-Then I'll go to take a shower first.

198
00:14:15,250 --> 00:14:16,130
Hello.

199
00:14:36,730 --> 00:14:37,800
Li Qing Tong.

200
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:38,760
She's not there.

201
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,960
When did she go out?

202
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:48,560
I don't know.
She wasn't here when I got up at 7 am.

203
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,930
You still don't like to say hello

204
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,850
as much as before.

205
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:26,210
How did you know I'm here?

206
00:15:29,380 --> 00:15:31,980
Right. I didn't expect you
to be in Linyang. Such a coincidence.

207
00:15:34,570 --> 00:15:36,450
Since I'm here,
let's have a meal together.

208
00:15:36,770 --> 00:15:38,200
I have to go home. I still have to review.

209
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:39,800
I can wait for you.

210
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,120
Jin Bu.

211
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,640
Hi.

212
00:16:05,730 --> 00:16:06,850
Long time no see.

213
00:16:07,410 --> 00:16:08,520
Long time no see.

214
00:16:09,250 --> 00:16:10,450
Why are you alone?

215
00:16:11,770 --> 00:16:13,200
Everyone is pretty busy.

216
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:14,770
I just came over and read the book myself.

217
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:19,680
Take it easy.

218
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:21,280
I won't send flowers this time.

219
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:25,850
Jin Bu.

220
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,920
Let me ask you a question.

221
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,600
Do you think

222
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:31,290
it's outdated

223
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,610
for a boy to send a girl flowers?

224
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:36,090
I think it's okay.

225
00:16:36,570 --> 00:16:38,030
Maybe I don't like it too much myself.

226
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,650
So what do you like?

227
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:42,160
I think

228
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:44,360
a boy can send a girl a scarf

229
00:16:44,450 --> 00:16:45,440
or gloves.

230
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:46,650
They're both pretty good.

231
00:16:47,130 --> 00:16:48,240
They are more practical than flowers.

232
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:51,840
It'd be very romantic
to send a sleigh on a snowy day.

233
00:16:51,930 --> 00:16:53,000
A sleigh?

234
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:55,810
An umbrella can be sent on rainy days.

235
00:17:00,680 --> 00:17:01,560
I got it.

236
00:17:02,210 --> 00:17:03,120
See you soon.

237
00:17:29,810 --> 00:17:31,240
Let me help you clean up first.

238
00:17:31,330 --> 00:17:32,450
No need.

239
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:33,800
Please sit.

240
00:18:00,490 --> 00:18:02,400
Why don't you live in school?

241
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:04,720
I don't like to live with other people.

242
00:18:06,850 --> 00:18:07,730
In fact,

243
00:18:08,210 --> 00:18:10,640
-everyone is quite worried about you...
-How about you go back first?

244
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,280
I have things to do.

245
00:18:15,650 --> 00:18:16,530
You go back first.

246
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:23,360
Then I'll see you next time.

247
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,370
No need.

248
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:25,720
Study hard

249
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,210
and leave me alone.

250
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,970
Why do you stare at me?

251
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,080
Don't you know?

252
00:19:30,410 --> 00:19:33,080
Every morning the alarm clock can't
wake you up even if it rings ten times.

253
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:34,500
You disappeared before dawn.

254
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:35,920
Where did you go?

255
00:19:40,050 --> 00:19:41,810
I went to see Wu Zhi Xun.

256
00:19:41,970 --> 00:19:42,960
Who?

257
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:50,560
Li Qing Tong, it's for you.

258
00:19:50,650 --> 00:19:52,370
-I'm coming.
-Then I'll go to take a shower first.

259
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,080
Hello.

260
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:58,160
[Is this Li Qing Tong?]

261
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,800
[I am Wu Zhi Xun's mother,]

262
00:20:00,090 --> 00:20:00,970
[Hu Yue.]

263
00:20:03,850 --> 00:20:05,000
It's... It's me.

264
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:07,640
What can I do for you?

265
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:10,160
[Have you seen Wu Zhi Xun lately?]

266
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,410
No.

267
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:17,120
[I thought he insisted on going
to Linyang to repeat his studies]

268
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,720
[because of you.]

269
00:20:18,810 --> 00:20:20,440
He's repeating his studies in Linyang?

270
00:20:20,530 --> 00:20:22,680
[Although he has resumed his studies,]

271
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:24,880
[he rarely goes to class]

272
00:20:25,290 --> 00:20:27,490
[and does not complete his homework.]

273
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:30,400
[His teacher has already called me
several times.]

274
00:20:30,890 --> 00:20:32,690
[But I don't dare to say much to him.]

275
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:35,770
[He is especially resistant to us now.]

276
00:20:36,210 --> 00:20:37,320
[I'm afraid that if I talk about it,]

277
00:20:37,410 --> 00:20:38,320
[he will again...]

278
00:20:40,010 --> 00:20:40,890
I...

279
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:44,210
Auntie, I just want to know why
he has turned out like this.

280
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,790
[I don't know how to say it either.]

281
00:20:48,330 --> 00:20:50,700
[I have only one presumptuous plea now.]

282
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:52,960
[I'd like you to visit him.]

283
00:20:53,690 --> 00:20:55,440
[He has only one friend,]

284
00:20:55,530 --> 00:20:56,560
[and that is you.]

285
00:20:56,650 --> 00:20:59,080
[He might just like to listen to you.]

286
00:20:59,170 --> 00:21:01,920
[So I'd like you to encourage him]

287
00:21:02,010 --> 00:21:04,050
[and cheer him up.]

288
00:21:04,490 --> 00:21:07,000
[You don't want to see him fall either,]

289
00:21:07,410 --> 00:21:08,330
[do you?]

290
00:21:09,730 --> 00:21:11,850
His mother told you to go see him,
so you went to see him?

291
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:14,080
Of course I had to go.

292
00:21:14,890 --> 00:21:15,890
In high school,

293
00:21:15,970 --> 00:21:16,920
how could I get into college

294
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:18,890
without Wu Zhi Xun?

295
00:21:19,290 --> 00:21:20,320
He is now like this.

296
00:21:20,410 --> 00:21:21,730
I definitely had to see him.

297
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:25,040
Then...

298
00:21:25,130 --> 00:21:27,080
Why didn't he take
the college entrance examination?

299
00:21:27,650 --> 00:21:29,530
Honestly, he didn't tell me.

300
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:33,050
But you don't even know
how dispirited he has become now.

301
00:21:33,290 --> 00:21:34,410
His house is very messy.

302
00:21:34,850 --> 00:21:36,840
You can't even imagine
that it's his house.

303
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:39,200
And he still doesn't want
to talk to people.

304
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:40,520
He doesn't even talk to me.

305
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,850
He immediately threw me out.

306
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:44,700
I really didn't expect

307
00:21:44,930 --> 00:21:47,370
Wu Zhi Xun to turn out like this one day.

308
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:49,280
It's incredible.

309
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:50,520
It can't be.

310
00:21:52,040 --> 00:21:53,590
I still have to go to him one more time.

311
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:55,050
I can't see him fall like this.

312
00:21:58,130 --> 00:22:00,080
You haven't eaten yet.

313
00:22:00,930 --> 00:22:04,330
[No. 1 Students' Dormitory]

314
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,000
What are you doing at this late hour?

315
00:22:07,090 --> 00:22:07,970
Dating.

316
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:18,880
Where is Li Qing Tong?

317
00:22:20,080 --> 00:22:21,370
She also went on a date.

318
00:22:23,810 --> 00:22:25,320
You have so many pen pals

319
00:22:25,410 --> 00:22:26,640
but none of them pursue you?

320
00:22:26,730 --> 00:22:28,440
We simply exchange literature.

321
00:22:32,610 --> 00:22:34,300
This pink one is a love letter.

322
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,510
This is my letter
and I haven't read it yet.

323
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:36,480
I'll look first.

324
00:22:42,690 --> 00:22:43,610
What is it written?

325
00:22:44,810 --> 00:22:46,330
To Li Jin Bu?

326
00:22:54,930 --> 00:22:55,840
["To Li Jin Bu.]

327
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:59,450
[It's the first time in my life
that I write a love letter to a girl.]

328
00:22:59,850 --> 00:23:01,120
[I don't know]

329
00:23:01,210 --> 00:23:02,440
[if it's love at first sight]

330
00:23:02,530 --> 00:23:03,880
[or love over time when it comes
to me liking you.]

331
00:23:04,250 --> 00:23:05,680
[After all, the first time we met,]

332
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,010
[it was a bit strange.]

333
00:23:07,690 --> 00:23:08,690
[But I'm happy.]

334
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:11,130
[We have a secret that belongs
to just the two of us.]

335
00:23:11,970 --> 00:23:14,030
[Your sudden appearance]

336
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:15,960
[made me panic a little]

337
00:23:16,050 --> 00:23:17,250
[and gave me the belief,
for the first time,]

338
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:20,570
[that I just wanted to be with a girl.]

339
00:23:21,570 --> 00:23:22,960
[I've done a lot of stupid things.]

340
00:23:23,040 --> 00:23:24,560
[I don't know what is right to say.]

341
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:25,840
[I don't have much to explain.]

342
00:23:25,930 --> 00:23:26,810
[It's fate.]

343
00:23:27,730 --> 00:23:28,990
[You've come to me.]

344
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:30,200
[Me behind you.]

345
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:32,560
[Although there are more and more
troubles daily]

346
00:23:32,650 --> 00:23:34,090
[I think it's worth it.]

347
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:36,000
[I looked forward to growing up.]

348
00:23:36,360 --> 00:23:38,410
[Because once we've grown up,
we could be together.]

349
00:23:38,730 --> 00:23:40,960
[I'd be able take your hand
and walk down every road.]

350
00:23:41,050 --> 00:23:42,400
[I wouldn't have to be separated
from you.]

351
00:23:42,570 --> 00:23:44,770
[I could say to the world
that this is my girlfriend.]

352
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,120
[Li Jin Bu.]

353
00:23:48,290 --> 00:23:50,440
[Don't turn away from me
just because you've grown up.]

354
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:51,720
[If so,]

355
00:23:51,810 --> 00:23:53,640
[I'd rather be a kid
for the rest of my life.]

356
00:23:54,690 --> 00:23:57,030
[All refusals are not
from your true heart.]

357
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,840
[It's true that you're good to me.]

358
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,720
[I've eaten the sandwiches you made.]

359
00:24:00,810 --> 00:24:02,520
[I've sat foolishly
by the side of the road with you.]

360
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:04,310
[I've taken you
through the streets and alleys.]]

361
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,880
[I've wiped your tears.]

362
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:08,330
[I have the unique bracelet
that you gave me.]

363
00:24:08,650 --> 00:24:08,850
[Hengdaohezi Welcomes You]

364
00:24:08,850 --> 00:24:10,840
[You and I have leant
against each other for warmth]

365
00:24:10,930 --> 00:24:12,250
[in a small train station
hundreds of kilometres away.]

366
00:24:12,610 --> 00:24:13,960
[I can help you make your wish come true.]

367
00:24:14,450 --> 00:24:15,520
[I am your aurora.]

368
00:24:16,250 --> 00:24:17,330
[I have heard a song.]

369
00:24:17,690 --> 00:24:18,600
[I'm giving it to you.]

370
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:20,000
[Heaven and Earth.]

371
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,560
[If it's really worth praising,]

372
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:23,480
[it is because of you]

373
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:25,450
[that they have become lively.]

374
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,520
[Li Jin Bu.]

375
00:24:26,690 --> 00:24:27,960
[We must be together.]

376
00:24:28,450 --> 00:24:29,560
[This is my fate.]

377
00:24:29,650 --> 00:24:30,850
[This is also your fate.]

378
00:24:32,210 --> 00:24:33,440
[So no matter what,]

379
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:34,880
[I will continue to persevere.]

380
00:24:35,370 --> 00:24:37,450
[Stick to everything
that makes you happy.]

381
00:24:38,050 --> 00:24:39,810
[I'm sure we can be together.]

382
00:24:40,330 --> 00:24:41,890
[If we have to be separated,]

383
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,560
[there will only be one reason.]

384
00:24:44,290 --> 00:24:45,170
[That is]

385
00:24:45,290 --> 00:24:47,440
[separation is also a thing
that can make you happy.]

386
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:49,890
[But I really want to be with you.]

387
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:51,480
[Even if we are not happy,]

388
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:52,970
[it does not matter.]

389
00:24:53,650 --> 00:24:55,200
[Your quasi-boyfriend.]

390
00:24:55,290 --> 00:24:56,170
[Duan Xiao.]

391
00:25:03,340 --> 00:25:04,210
That's all.

392
00:25:04,330 --> 00:25:05,880
Guys. Class is over.

393
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:09,880
Chen Jun He.

394
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,440
I'll ask you something.

395
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:14,210
Have you still been in touch
with Duan Xiao recently?

396
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:15,720
Yes.

397
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,030
So can you get him to come over?

398
00:25:17,120 --> 00:25:18,210
I have something to say to him.

399
00:25:18,410 --> 00:25:19,320
He can't come.

400
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:21,960
-Why?
-He went to a hands-on activity.

401
00:25:22,050 --> 00:25:23,280
He won't be back for a few weeks.

402
00:25:24,330 --> 00:25:26,130
When exactly will he be back?

403
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:27,960
I don't know about that.

404
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:29,670
Cell phone reception is bad there.

405
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:31,000
His phone can't be reached either.

406
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:33,200
We can only wait for him
to come back and contact us.

407
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:36,260
Well,

408
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:37,390
when he comes back,

409
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:39,000
I'll tell you, okay?

410
00:25:42,810 --> 00:25:43,840
Then...

411
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,560
Li Qing Tong...

412
00:25:46,650 --> 00:25:48,040
Recently...

413
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:49,570
Never mind.

414
00:26:29,490 --> 00:26:30,400
Hello?

415
00:26:33,250 --> 00:26:34,210
It's for you.

416
00:26:45,330 --> 00:26:48,210
Wu Zhi Xun. I know you're at
home. Open the door, please.

417
00:26:48,970 --> 00:26:50,080
Open the door, please.

418
00:26:50,170 --> 00:26:51,690
I know you must be home.

419
00:26:53,330 --> 00:26:54,330
Wu Zhi Xun.

420
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:00,170
You are indeed at home.

421
00:27:00,730 --> 00:27:02,600
I thought you were at school
during the day.

422
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:05,120
I waited for you in front of the school
for more than three hours.

423
00:27:05,210 --> 00:27:06,600
Why are you here again?

424
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,120
I...

425
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,560
I've come to treat you for dinner.

426
00:27:15,890 --> 00:27:17,810
Why don't you eat?

427
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:19,920
Eat, please.

428
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:21,290
I have no appetite.

429
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,720
I know what you want to ask.

430
00:27:36,290 --> 00:27:38,250
So can you tell me?

431
00:27:40,970 --> 00:27:42,090
I want to get revenge on them.

432
00:27:44,530 --> 00:27:46,250
The reason I didn't take
the college entrance examination

433
00:27:47,570 --> 00:27:49,400
is that I wanted
to get back at my parents.

434
00:27:52,130 --> 00:27:53,010
Waiter.

435
00:27:53,130 --> 00:27:54,210
A beer, please.

436
00:28:06,170 --> 00:28:07,560
For eighteen years,

437
00:28:08,810 --> 00:28:11,250
I have lived the way they asked me to.

438
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:13,600
They don't want me to stay in this county.

439
00:28:14,890 --> 00:28:17,480
They want me to go out
in the most honourable way.

440
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,370
So my life

441
00:28:19,850 --> 00:28:21,400
should only be about studying,

442
00:28:21,490 --> 00:28:22,370
taking exams,

443
00:28:23,010 --> 00:28:24,480
winning awards and getting ahead.

444
00:28:24,570 --> 00:28:27,680
I shouldn't make friends with those
no-good kids in this small county.

445
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:29,760
I still have to see the big world.

446
00:28:30,530 --> 00:28:32,690
I need to fulfill
their unfulfilled dreams.

447
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:34,610
If I can't do it well,

448
00:28:34,890 --> 00:28:36,080
I will be a piece of trash

449
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,970
and a loser who's sorry
for their dedication and hopes.

450
00:28:39,890 --> 00:28:41,410
Does it sound miserable?

451
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:44,880
Maybe...

452
00:28:46,010 --> 00:28:47,760
They did that for your sake.

453
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:48,720
Do you know

454
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:51,560
how I was treated back home

455
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,170
after I arrived first at school?

456
00:28:56,130 --> 00:28:57,400
I had to stand for three hours
as a punishment.

457
00:28:57,600 --> 00:28:58,650
Why?

458
00:28:58,890 --> 00:29:00,160
Because my dad said

459
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,290
he could see pride in my eyes.

460
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,640
In this low-level high school
of this small county,

461
00:29:05,730 --> 00:29:07,450
being the top student is not something
to be proud of at all.

462
00:29:08,050 --> 00:29:09,080
So,

463
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,640
they wanted to give me,
a man with no ambition,

464
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,360
a proper punishment.

465
00:29:14,330 --> 00:29:15,730
This is what they do for me.

466
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,730
This is too much.

467
00:29:18,130 --> 00:29:19,690
So now you understand

468
00:29:20,050 --> 00:29:21,770
why I did it, right?

469
00:29:26,360 --> 00:29:28,410
So now you're done.

470
00:29:28,850 --> 00:29:30,890
You can still take another year.

471
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:34,200
Your grades are so good, you can surely
get into a good college.

472
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:35,240
It's impossible.

473
00:29:36,170 --> 00:29:37,290
I don't know why

474
00:29:39,050 --> 00:29:40,570
since I started repeating my studies,

475
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:43,400
I feel sick

476
00:29:43,690 --> 00:29:45,010
when I see those notes,

477
00:29:45,970 --> 00:29:47,360
exercises and papers.

478
00:29:47,970 --> 00:29:49,880
I don't want to read,

479
00:29:49,970 --> 00:29:52,050
write nor listen to a word of it
right now.

480
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:54,520
Now, my parents don't even know

481
00:29:55,450 --> 00:29:57,090
that I haven't been to school
for three days

482
00:29:57,600 --> 00:29:59,330
and haven't taken a practice exam.

483
00:30:00,650 --> 00:30:01,880
It shouldn't be long

484
00:30:02,930 --> 00:30:04,200
before I'm expelled from school.

485
00:30:05,010 --> 00:30:05,890
In fact,

486
00:30:07,090 --> 00:30:08,410
they already know it.

487
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,440
Wu Zhi Xun.

488
00:30:14,730 --> 00:30:16,660
I'm not very good at talking either.

489
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:19,650
I don't know how to comfort you either.

490
00:30:20,010 --> 00:30:21,410
You don't need to comfort me.

491
00:30:22,490 --> 00:30:23,810
It's been a long time

492
00:30:24,610 --> 00:30:26,890
since I've talked to someone so much.

493
00:30:27,490 --> 00:30:28,400
I remember

494
00:30:29,210 --> 00:30:31,600
the last time I droned on so much

495
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:35,000
was also with you.

496
00:30:40,450 --> 00:30:41,360
You did talk a lot

497
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:43,440
when you used to

498
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,920
teach me to study hard.

499
00:30:48,290 --> 00:30:51,650
Then you can always tell me anything
you want to say in the future.

500
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,120
No need.

501
00:31:00,250 --> 00:31:01,520
Study hard.

502
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:02,920
I'll leave.

503
00:31:04,230 --> 00:31:05,350
Won't you eat?

504
00:31:18,490 --> 00:31:19,360
Hello?

505
00:31:19,450 --> 00:31:21,010
[Hello. I am Chen Jun He.]

506
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:23,500
What's up?

507
00:31:23,570 --> 00:31:24,450
[Li Jin Bu.]

508
00:31:24,810 --> 00:31:27,090
[There's something I need to tell you.]

509
00:31:27,530 --> 00:31:28,640
[Duan Xiao]

510
00:31:28,730 --> 00:31:30,880
was supposed to return
from his internship yesterday.

511
00:31:30,970 --> 00:31:32,230
But I haven't even seen him today.

512
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:33,550
Have you called him yet?

513
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:34,560
[Yes.]

514
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:35,810
[But I can't get through.]

515
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:39,120
The place where
he interns is very isolated.

516
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:40,960
I worry...

517
00:31:41,050 --> 00:31:42,050
[what if...]

518
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,000
What's wrong?

519
00:31:59,090 --> 00:32:00,160
What happened?

520
00:32:11,840 --> 00:32:14,000
Li Jin Bu,
please turn off the alarm clock.

521
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,280
Li Jin Bu.

522
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:32,590
Turn it off.

523
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,870
Hello. Is Duan Xiao from this dormitory?

524
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,130
You must be Li Jin Bu.

525
00:32:45,210 --> 00:32:46,160
How do you know that?

526
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:48,850
Everyone in our dormitory
knows Li Jin Bu.

527
00:32:49,050 --> 00:32:51,200
Duan Xiao tells us every day
that he has a girlfriend

528
00:32:51,290 --> 00:32:52,520
and you have a very good relationship.

529
00:32:53,130 --> 00:32:54,160
This is Duan Xiao's location.

530
00:32:54,250 --> 00:32:55,130
Come on.

531
00:33:51,570 --> 00:33:53,080
How come Duan Xiao is not back yet?

532
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:55,030
His bracelet falls there.

533
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,720
We told him to come back but he didn't.

534
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:58,120
He wants to be there to find it.

535
00:33:58,560 --> 00:33:59,930
So when will he be back?

536
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:01,720
It is reasonable to say that
he buys a ticket for today

537
00:34:01,810 --> 00:34:03,450
and should arrive soon.

538
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:19,440
Hello.

539
00:34:19,610 --> 00:34:21,550
Have buses from Shanze arrived?

540
00:34:21,639 --> 00:34:22,639
They are all late.

541
00:34:22,730 --> 00:34:24,449
One had an accident.

542
00:34:27,530 --> 00:34:28,889
One from Shanze?

543
00:34:29,409 --> 00:34:30,290
Yes.

544
00:34:34,690 --> 00:34:36,830
Hello, I want a ticket to Shanze.

545
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:38,570
There are no more tickets.
The last bus has already left.

546
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:42,330
[Ticket Office]

547
00:34:50,850 --> 00:34:51,730
Duan Xiao.

548
00:34:53,850 --> 00:34:54,730
Duan Xiao.

549
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,480
What's wrong with you?

550
00:35:08,570 --> 00:35:10,510
Can you drive me to Beicheng Highway?

551
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:12,240
You can't go there.
There's been a car accident.

552
00:35:12,330 --> 00:35:13,920
-The road is closed there.
-I have something very urgent.

553
00:35:14,010 --> 00:35:15,640
I beg you. Let me go.

554
00:35:15,730 --> 00:35:17,320
-I'm off.
-Please.

555
00:35:17,410 --> 00:35:19,050
I beg you. Please.

556
00:35:38,820 --> 00:35:43,400
[Linyang - Shanze]

557
00:35:58,450 --> 00:35:59,330
Hua.

558
00:36:08,770 --> 00:36:09,850
Why are you here?

559
00:36:39,930 --> 00:36:41,040
[Being together]

560
00:36:41,130 --> 00:36:43,090
is really the best thing in this world.]

561
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:47,240
[Wang Li Hong]

562
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:51,570
[The people who return from the old days]

563
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:54,360
[seem to have never been deleted
from the memory.]

564
00:36:55,210 --> 00:36:56,240
[And those regrets]

565
00:36:56,330 --> 00:36:57,760
[that don't come to fruition]

566
00:36:58,170 --> 00:37:00,130
[are waiting for the chance
to start over,]

567
00:37:03,570 --> 00:37:04,530
[or,]

568
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:06,920
[to turn into bigger regrets.]

569
00:37:12,890 --> 00:37:14,960
[But this time
I don't want to think so much.]

570
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,680
[I want to be with you.]

571
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:18,610
[Even if we are unhappy,]

572
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:21,850
[even if more unexpected things happen,]

573
00:37:22,610 --> 00:37:24,010
[it will be fine.]

574
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:40,350
Let's get to know each other again.

575
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:41,410
This is my girlfriend,

576
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,530
Li Jin Bu.

577
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:44,040
This is my boyfriend, Duan Xiao.

578
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:47,260
Please take care of us
carefully afterwards.

579
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:01,150
What is going on with you guys?

580
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:02,680
Why are you suddenly together?

581
00:38:02,770 --> 00:38:03,910
I just figured out

582
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,920
that if we like each other,
we should be together.

583
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,960
We can't control the outcome anyway,

584
00:38:08,050 --> 00:38:08,930
so the process is the most important.

585
00:38:09,250 --> 00:38:10,370
I don't think about it that much.

586
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,160
You should have thought of it that way
a long time ago.

587
00:38:12,250 --> 00:38:13,720
I advised you many times.

588
00:38:14,850 --> 00:38:15,790
You too.

589
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:18,640
You should enjoy the process first
and live your life the way you want.

590
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:21,720
You're right.

591
00:38:22,010 --> 00:38:22,960
Then I'll go back to him.

592
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:28,440
Leaving again...

593
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:31,720
How is it?

594
00:38:32,050 --> 00:38:32,930
Is it accurate?

595
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:34,770
You are not be loyal to me.

596
00:38:35,250 --> 00:38:36,770
Why do you say that?

597
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:38,760
You don't know?

598
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:41,320
Didn't we agree to be
a brotherly alliance to advance together?

599
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:43,080
You are actually
one step ahead of other people.

600
00:38:43,570 --> 00:38:45,270
It is also something I didn't expect.

601
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:46,520
She's the one who took the initiative
to confess her love to me.

602
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,730
Then I couldn't say to her,

603
00:38:48,170 --> 00:38:50,360
Wait for Chen Jun He,
and we fall in love together then.

604
00:38:50,610 --> 00:38:51,490
Right?

605
00:38:53,130 --> 00:38:54,010
I won't play.

606
00:38:55,890 --> 00:38:56,770
You...

607
00:38:59,650 --> 00:39:01,530
Why are you a little angry?

608
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:04,640
Let me take you somewhere.

609
00:39:04,930 --> 00:39:05,810
I won't go.

610
00:39:06,370 --> 00:39:07,450
Let's go.

611
00:39:20,240 --> 00:39:21,160
How's this place?

612
00:39:21,850 --> 00:39:24,000
Two men here?

613
00:39:24,090 --> 00:39:25,040
Forget it.

614
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:26,000
Let's go.

615
00:39:30,010 --> 00:39:31,210
Here I am again.

616
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:32,480
What's wrong?

617
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,280
I just came to see you.

618
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,640
I brought you some fruit.

619
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:05,920
Thank you.

620
00:40:06,010 --> 00:40:06,890
Qing Tong.

621
00:40:07,040 --> 00:40:08,970
You're welcome.
I'm happy when you're happy.

622
00:40:14,050 --> 00:40:15,010
Li Qing Tong.

623
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:17,240
Li Qing Tong.

624
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:22,640
If you have nothing to do, go back early.

625
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:29,360
Come on, I just got here.

626
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:35,600
I'd better help you clean up.

627
00:40:35,690 --> 00:40:36,960
No need.

628
00:40:38,650 --> 00:40:39,600
It's okay.

629
00:40:39,770 --> 00:40:41,090
I happen to have no lessons
in the afternoon.

630
00:40:41,230 --> 00:40:42,270
How about this? You play games

631
00:40:42,410 --> 00:40:43,290
and I clean up.

632
00:41:09,490 --> 00:41:11,960
You should drink less.

633
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:13,110
This is not good for your health.

634
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,680
It's too late.

635
00:41:14,770 --> 00:41:15,880
Go back early.

636
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,880
I won't go back.

637
00:41:25,120 --> 00:41:26,280
I'm going to review now.

638
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:28,410
If you stay here, I can't review.
